Further investigation reveals that the _jsp.java file produced from one of the problematic jsps with Tomcat 6.0.28 is:
    _jspx_th_c_005fset_005f0.setValue((java.lang.Object) org.apache.jasper.runtime.PageContextImpl.proprietaryEvaluate("${basic_form}", java.lang.Object.class, (PageContext)_jspx_page_context, null, false));

Tomcat 7.0.12:
    _jspx_th_c_005fset_005f0.setValue(new String("${basic_form}"));
